1. *Heroj* je spasio živote sedam ljudi. (The hero saved the lives of seven people.)

2. Njegova hrabra odluka postala je *heroj* u očima mnogih. (His brave decision became a hero in the eyes of many.)

3. On je *heroj* koji je uspeo da se usprotivi pritisku društva. (He is the hero who managed to stand up to the pressure of society.)

4. Njegova odvažnost je činila od njega pravog *heroja*. (His courage made him a true hero.)

5. On je postao *heroj* u očima svoje dece. (He became a hero in the eyes of his children.)